{"tid":463380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家植人腦組織入老鼠腦　掀道德爭議","createTime":"2017-11-09T12:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T00:55:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":112,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"976a60fa298da6cdf2c2988cceaecadbb26721d0","tid":463380,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171109/s00005/4406b0fdf653661d79b5342ad0822937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171109%2Fs00005%2F4406b0fdf653661d79b5342ad0822937.jpg&h=80419fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為研究不同疾病對人體的影響及找出治療方法，科學家過去已不時使用各種生理上與人體相似的動物進行實驗。近日更有研究團隊表示，成功將人類腦組織植入老鼠腦部，植入的組織甚至成功與老鼠腦組織連結，掀起一番道德爭議，議題將於本周六（11日）起在美國華盛頓舉行的神經科學學會中討論。<br />\n<br />\n奧地利維也納的科學家近4年前發現，可以利用幹細胞培育出被稱為「類器官」（organoids）、大小有如扁豆的人腦組織，有助他們研究人類腦部發展及阿茲海默症和寨卡等影響腦部的疾病。<br />\n<br />\n過去這些人腦類器官僅存在於試管內，直至剛過去的周末&mdash;&mdash;兩隊神經科學家團隊均報告，他們成功將這些組織植入老鼠腦部。科學家嘗試以光線照射實驗鼠眼睛時，更發現植入的人腦類器官出現神經活動。其他實驗團隊則指，成功將人腦類器官連接到老鼠血管。<br />\n<br />\n其實過去已有研究人員，以老鼠培育出人類耳朵及皮膚，亦有科學家研究以人豬混合胚胎培育人類器官，以解決移植器官短缺問題，但今次將人腦組織植入老鼠腦，依然掀起道德爭議。有學者質疑，在道德上有什麼理由，准許人類以老鼠進行實驗，進而擔心人腦組織在老鼠腦部發展，會對實驗鼠的智力有何影響，甚至會否引起牠們的「身分認同」問題，以至終有一天，這些人腦類器官會令被植入的老鼠覺得自己是「被困在老鼠體內的人類」。<br />\n<br />\n美國西雅圖腦科學研究所「Allen Institute for Brain Science」所長高治（Christof Koch）直言：「科學發展得太迅速，道德標準已經跟不上了。」"},{"pid":"3e21f6071e9e85e287c9773298b42ee2877f0d8f","tid":463380,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00005/1510224644742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00005%2F1510224644742&d=u2V4FAe0VNi%2BBpfrTfl2yNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e2bffe12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00005%2F1510224644742&h=306467d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00005/1510224644742</a>"},{"pid":"6ada5838c3a8bafe6df819243737eedfc80efc8b","tid":463380,"uid":85924,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"政府私底下應該做勁多呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f7f697e17c2ee33390866f757178806d1b998b","tid":463380,"uid":114097,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府私底下應該做勁多呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n國土練成陣"},{"pid":"0c196a404f2dead9fe0aa66776214526b194a90f","tid":463380,"uid":31637,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"鋼鍊劇情成真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f93b3b409a1a724805ef1af4c9b526d2819569b","tid":463380,"uid":71579,"like":162,"dislike":5,"score":157,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"唔用老鼠唔通用人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0da83476083279d8c147bfb671a096564f7bdc2","tid":463380,"uid":61034,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"來自新世界"},{"pid":"8e070692431c84c269cb6485d0f2a2b77b3776c3","tid":463380,"uid":51134,"like":120,"dislike":3,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"哥。。。哥哥。。"},{"pid":"67fc0f94f93c195793a9b15809ccd7dda92a27a0","tid":463380,"uid":34023,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用老鼠唔通用人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成功就用人嫁啦<br />\n不過佢講果個身份自覺個情況都幾得人驚<br />\n好似拍戲咁"},{"pid":"be7f470ee5fac4f6f84a18e8d89f4d3ef061952d","tid":463380,"uid":73722,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"班友既ff能力屌打九成連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\